snippet.title: Duke Nukem Time to Kill - Game Trailer
snippet.description: Trailer for the playstation game, Duke nukem Time to Kill as featured on the Rogue Trip game disc.  The video is nearly the same as the intro video to the game, but the HUD is different.  The song playing is also played during the credits after finishing the game.  Some reviews called the game "duke raider" because of the blocky level design and similar gameplay.
